WEBVTT

01:31.380 --> 01:34.900
=Generation to Generation=

01:35.020 --> 01:37.940
=Episode 36=

01:46.380 --> 01:47.220
Lingbo.

01:50.490 --> 01:51.396
She's still breathing.

01:57.210 --> 01:58.050
Mu Qingyan.

02:02.380 --> 02:05.020
You found this place so soon.

02:06.050 --> 02:07.980
Yuzhi told you, didn't he?

02:16.380 --> 02:17.380
Since you're here,

02:18.060 --> 02:19.220
neither of you can leave.

02:19.890 --> 02:21.380
So, the man in black really is you.

02:22.060 --> 02:23.170
I've always had a question.

02:23.820 --> 02:25.500
You hate the Yins so much.

02:26.410 --> 02:27.820
Why keep Song Yuzhi?

02:28.890 --> 02:30.260
Isn't he Yin Dai's grandson?

02:30.690 --> 02:31.570
He is different.

02:33.340 --> 02:35.540
He grew up by my side,

02:35.540 --> 02:37.010
personally taught by me.

02:37.010 --> 02:38.290
He is not only gifted

02:38.290 --> 02:39.780
but also refined and outstanding.

02:39.780 --> 02:41.290
And he acts with composure,

02:42.010 --> 02:43.660
upright and honorable.

02:44.380 --> 02:45.500
He's the most suitable match

02:46.060 --> 02:47.820
for Zhao.

02:47.820 --> 02:49.290
Stop putting on this act.

02:50.660 --> 02:51.890
Everything you've done

02:52.820 --> 02:55.220
was to find the Jade Sunflower
for cultivation.

02:56.060 --> 02:57.873
After returning empty-handed
from Chang Fort,

02:58.820 --> 03:00.890
you lured Wu Gang to cultivate
the Nether Aura,

03:01.500 --> 03:02.820
causing Song Yuzhi to be poisoned.

03:03.780 --> 03:04.940
Because you knew

03:04.940 --> 03:06.610
Zhao and Song Yuzhi were close.

03:06.610 --> 03:08.380
She'd never stand by and do nothing.

03:08.380 --> 03:10.060
The final clue to the Jade Sunflower

03:10.060 --> 03:11.010
was in Luoying Valley.

03:11.940 --> 03:13.220
Only by doing this

03:13.220 --> 03:15.940
might the Jade Sunflower,
missing for over a decade,

03:15.940 --> 03:17.290
reappear in the world.

03:19.100 --> 03:20.290
Lord Qi,

03:20.290 --> 03:21.340
you keep saying

03:21.340 --> 03:22.940
it's for Song Yuzhi and Zhao's good.

03:23.690 --> 03:25.730
But you've been using them all along.

03:25.730 --> 03:27.130
There's no point talking to you.

03:27.540 --> 03:28.410
Everything I've done

03:29.380 --> 03:31.290
is for a great cause.

03:32.660 --> 03:33.730
What great cause?

03:33.730 --> 03:34.940
What revenge?

03:34.940 --> 03:36.380
What reshaping Jianghu?

03:36.380 --> 03:37.850
In the end,

03:37.850 --> 03:39.780
it's just sacrificing others' lives

03:39.780 --> 03:40.820
for your selfish desires.

03:41.500 --> 03:42.540
How are you

03:42.980 --> 03:44.730
any different from Yin Dai?

03:44.730 --> 03:46.100
So what?

03:59.100 --> 04:00.540
The Sevens Poison.

04:00.540 --> 04:01.850
When did you poison him?

04:01.850 --> 04:02.850
Back at Xuankong Nunnery.

04:11.170 --> 04:12.010
Watch out!

04:16.580 --> 04:18.260
Why does the poison
have no effect on you?

04:18.780 --> 04:20.730
I have the Tianhuo Dragon Bone.

04:21.580 --> 04:22.966
All poisons are useless against me.

04:24.290 --> 04:26.810
You two can't stop me.

04:26.810 --> 04:28.540
Since you are immune to poison,

04:28.540 --> 04:29.930
why could Wu Gang

04:29.930 --> 04:31.580
switch you?

04:35.290 --> 04:36.660
You were never poisoned.

04:37.250 --> 04:38.660
From beginning to end,

04:38.660 --> 04:39.700
you were just pretending.

04:40.290 --> 04:41.580
You allowed Wu Gang and Wu Xiong

04:41.580 --> 04:42.850
to go to the sect.

04:42.850 --> 04:44.170
Did you also arrange

04:44.170 --> 04:45.730
Ms. Luo's appearance

04:45.730 --> 04:46.900
at the memorial?

04:47.700 --> 04:48.540
That's right.

04:49.580 --> 04:51.340
I wanted to use Luo Yuanrong

04:52.370 --> 04:54.170
to tear apart Yin Dai's false mask.

04:55.020 --> 04:56.850
But I never expected

04:56.850 --> 04:59.780
Nie Zhe to fish in troubled waters,

04:59.780 --> 05:01.730
using Qianmian Sect to stir up trouble.

05:01.730 --> 05:03.250
So, I went along with the plan.

05:04.050 --> 05:05.140
Just in time

05:05.140 --> 05:07.170
to dampen the spirit of the Six Sects.

05:07.170 --> 05:08.810
So, you kept pretending

05:09.610 --> 05:11.220
until I helped you retrieve the saliva.

05:11.900 --> 05:12.740
Zhao,

05:13.410 --> 05:15.020
I didn't want you to take risks.

05:15.980 --> 05:17.100
But I had no choice.

05:17.580 --> 05:18.730
In this world,

05:18.730 --> 05:20.170
only the Cais

05:20.170 --> 05:22.050
can find the saliva.

05:22.050 --> 05:23.730
Only after obtaining it

05:23.730 --> 05:26.050
can I cultivate the Ziwei Method

05:26.050 --> 05:27.370
and avenge your aunt.

05:28.170 --> 05:30.540
No wonder the Body Shift was so strange.

05:31.540 --> 05:33.050
But after all your calculations,

05:33.050 --> 05:35.580
you didn't expect Zhao to go
to Li Sect to help me

05:35.580 --> 05:37.370
and to learn about the man in black.

05:37.850 --> 05:40.220
If Zhao and Yuzhi
hadn't been there that day,

05:40.220 --> 05:41.340
I would've killed you.

05:42.900 --> 05:45.100
If I'd killed you then,

05:45.100 --> 05:46.700
nothing would've happened.

05:46.700 --> 05:47.860
Though you failed to kill me,

05:48.850 --> 05:50.290
you killed Sun Ruoshui to silence her

05:51.020 --> 05:52.140
and rescued Nie Zhe.

05:52.780 --> 05:54.250
The ambush at the Chang graveyard

05:55.140 --> 05:56.810
and the attack by the riverside

05:57.660 --> 05:59.410
were done by your men.

05:59.410 --> 06:00.810
No wonder those assassins

06:00.810 --> 06:01.900
kept showing mercy to Zhao,

06:03.170 --> 06:04.580
yet struck at me with killing blows.

06:05.930 --> 06:07.656
Unfortunately,
Zhao was soft-hearted then

06:07.667 --> 06:09.567
and refused to believe
it was done by her sect.

06:10.290 --> 06:11.540
Later on,

06:11.540 --> 06:13.810
you used Song Xiuzhi
to throw Guangtian Sect into chaos.

06:13.810 --> 06:16.100
Not only to weaken their strength,

06:16.100 --> 06:17.740
but also to lure Zhao

06:17.751 --> 06:19.153
into going to the Blood Marsh Forest

06:19.700 --> 06:20.810
to find the Night Orchid.

06:21.290 --> 06:23.942
You also ordered Song Xiuzhi to use

06:23.953 --> 06:25.220
the poisoned dart on Song Yuzhi.

06:25.220 --> 06:27.250
I told Song Xiuzhi

06:27.250 --> 06:29.020
not to harm Yuzhi's life.

06:29.580 --> 06:31.540
You still don't understand humans.

06:32.250 --> 06:33.900
Song Xiuzhi is narrow-minded.

06:34.540 --> 06:35.506
How could he show mercy?

06:36.580 --> 06:38.340
If Zhao hadn't risked her life
to save him,

06:38.980 --> 06:40.900
Song Yuzhi would already be dead.

06:42.580 --> 06:44.100
Mr. Chang once said

06:44.100 --> 06:45.900
that selfish desires

06:45.900 --> 06:48.100
lead to countless mistakes.

06:48.100 --> 06:49.610
In fact,

06:49.610 --> 06:50.980
before Mr. Chang died,

06:50.980 --> 06:53.140
he already suspected Qingque Sect.

06:53.140 --> 06:55.020
And he vaguely sensed

06:55.020 --> 06:56.930
who the mastermind

06:56.930 --> 06:58.340
behind everything was.

06:58.340 --> 06:59.860
The one who leaked the Six Sects' info

06:59.871 --> 07:01.194
and exposed Yin Dai's whereabouts

07:01.205 --> 07:02.762
(Chang Fort)
should be the same person.

07:02.773 --> 07:03.810
After Pingshu died,

07:05.410 --> 07:06.850
Nie Zhe began making moves again.

07:06.850 --> 07:09.340
There seemed to be an insider.

07:10.100 --> 07:11.540
I secretly investigated one by one.

07:11.540 --> 07:13.100
Only one person was the most suspicious.

07:13.100 --> 07:15.370
He had deep ties to Qingque Sect.

07:15.370 --> 07:16.290
But

07:17.290 --> 07:19.020
since Uncle Chang suspected Master,

07:19.580 --> 07:20.900
why did he entrust you to Master

07:21.490 --> 07:22.850
before he died?

07:22.850 --> 07:24.050
The most dangerous place

07:24.930 --> 07:26.370
is the safest place.

07:28.250 --> 07:29.850
Mr. Mu,

07:29.850 --> 07:31.810
I can no longer protect you.

07:31.810 --> 07:34.100
The only place that can keep you safe

07:34.100 --> 07:35.250
is Qingque Sect.

07:35.970 --> 07:36.810
Remember:

07:36.810 --> 07:39.580
You're my son Chang Ning.

07:47.100 --> 07:48.140
Mr. Chang

07:48.140 --> 07:49.220
realized Lord Qi

07:49.220 --> 07:51.580
had noticed the secret investigation.

07:51.580 --> 07:53.100
So, before his death,

07:53.100 --> 07:54.766
without showing
the slightest hesitation,

07:54.777 --> 07:56.490
he entrusted his only son
to Qingque Sect.

07:56.490 --> 07:58.610
Only then could he dispel
Lord Qi's suspicions.

07:59.250 --> 08:01.370
I underestimated Chang.

08:03.810 --> 08:04.700
Master.

08:06.780 --> 08:07.620
Zhao.

08:08.850 --> 08:09.700
I know

08:09.700 --> 08:11.580
everything you've done was for Aunt.

08:13.610 --> 08:15.020
It's enough already.

08:15.020 --> 08:15.980
Stop.

08:16.850 --> 08:17.690
No.

08:18.220 --> 08:20.370
My cultivation is about to succeed.

08:20.810 --> 08:22.700
Then, I'll be invincible in the world,

08:23.540 --> 08:24.810
with no one to fear.

08:25.410 --> 08:26.290
I'll hold

08:26.290 --> 08:27.290
a grand wedding

08:28.490 --> 08:30.730
for you and Yuzhi.

08:30.730 --> 08:31.570
All right?

08:47.890 --> 08:49.940
Oh, no. He's reaching the final level.

08:50.940 --> 08:51.780
Master.

08:52.010 --> 08:53.100
Master!

08:53.100 --> 08:54.650
She's your daughter!

10:30.940 --> 10:32.180
This is Qingque Sect.

10:33.010 --> 10:33.940
What are you doing?

10:34.420 --> 10:35.340
Rebelling?

10:35.340 --> 10:36.220
Yang Heying!

10:50.700 --> 10:51.940
What are you doing here?

10:52.340 --> 10:53.820
Naturally, to settle grievances

10:54.300 --> 10:55.370
and take revenge.

10:57.730 --> 10:59.340
Lord Cai, Lady Ning,

10:59.340 --> 11:00.980
go find Zhao first.

11:00.980 --> 11:02.010
After I finish my father,

11:02.010 --> 11:03.220
I'll go meet you.

11:04.490 --> 11:05.350
Xiaolan,

11:05.420 --> 11:07.100
let us deal with him for you.

11:07.700 --> 11:08.890
Let me do it.

11:09.253 --> 11:11.053
I want to avenge my mother
with my own hands.

11:11.490 --> 11:12.330
Don't act recklessly.

11:13.340 --> 11:14.180
Shangguan,

11:14.420 --> 11:15.700
stay here and support Xiaolan.

11:16.300 --> 11:17.340
Don't worry.

11:18.300 --> 11:19.650
None of you will escape.

11:20.100 --> 11:20.940
Attack!

11:39.490 --> 11:40.890
You think you can take revenge?

11:51.700 --> 11:52.980
Storm Axe Blade.

11:52.980 --> 11:54.730
My grandfather's famous weapon.

11:55.770 --> 11:57.300
After he was injured and retired,

11:57.300 --> 11:58.966
he secretly had someone
deliver it to me.

11:59.700 --> 12:01.340
He told me to train diligently.

12:01.340 --> 12:02.542
He said that even as a woman,

12:02.553 --> 12:04.340
one should have a world of her own,

12:04.340 --> 12:05.940
just like Ms. Cai.

12:05.940 --> 12:07.060
What nonsense.

12:07.060 --> 12:08.580
Who'd draw a blade at their father?

12:09.250 --> 12:11.180
You are worse than beasts.

12:11.180 --> 12:13.490
You brought it upon yourself.

12:19.850 --> 12:20.980
Yang Heying,

12:20.980 --> 12:21.890
please.

12:27.420 --> 12:28.260
Yuzhi.

12:28.850 --> 12:30.060
The grudges between us

12:31.340 --> 12:33.180
should be settled by ourselves.

12:33.730 --> 12:34.980
Father is still alive.

12:35.370 --> 12:37.180
He's still the Lord of Guangtian Sect.

12:37.180 --> 12:39.010
Are you planning to defy him?

12:39.010 --> 12:39.850
Ridiculous.

12:39.850 --> 12:41.430
You betrayed your master and ancestors.

12:41.441 --> 12:42.847
You are no longer part of our sect.

12:43.420 --> 12:44.610
The Lord's token is here.

12:44.980 --> 12:46.610
It represents the Lord.

12:46.833 --> 12:48.552
The Lord is recuperating
in Luoying Valley.

12:48.563 --> 12:49.683
He will soon recover.

12:50.250 --> 12:52.220
Then, he'll surely settle accounts
with you,

12:52.220 --> 12:54.220
the traitor who harmed his family.

12:54.220 --> 12:55.060
Shut up!

12:55.610 --> 12:56.980
I've defeated Song Yuzhi.

12:57.420 --> 12:58.820
I am the new Lord.

12:58.820 --> 13:00.420
Last time, my injuries had not healed.

13:00.420 --> 13:01.300
Xiuzhi,

13:01.300 --> 13:02.980
do you dare compete again?

13:03.850 --> 13:04.850
Bring it on.

14:17.340 --> 14:18.420
You really want to kill me?

14:18.890 --> 14:19.730
Don't worry.

14:20.610 --> 14:21.850
After you die,

14:21.850 --> 14:23.580
I'll raise my little brother.

14:24.700 --> 14:25.820
He was born weak.

14:25.820 --> 14:27.850
He can't cultivate
advanced martial arts anyway.

14:27.850 --> 14:30.130
I'll have someone teach him
reading and writing.

14:30.130 --> 14:31.700
He can live as a humble farmer.

14:33.340 --> 14:35.650
As for the lord position of Siqi Sect,

14:36.130 --> 14:37.300
I'll take it.

14:38.850 --> 14:40.980
Surely, many elders will oppose it.

14:40.980 --> 14:42.420
But that doesn't matter.

14:42.420 --> 14:44.700
I'll make them submit one by one.

14:44.700 --> 14:46.469
All these years,
when you committed crimes,

14:46.480 --> 14:48.130
they said nothing.

14:48.130 --> 14:50.010
So, when I become the Lord,

14:50.010 --> 14:52.300
why should they jump out
with righteous speeches?

14:52.980 --> 14:53.820
Father,

14:54.650 --> 14:55.490
don't you think so?

14:56.330 --> 14:57.180
Xiaolan,

14:57.180 --> 14:58.420
I am your father.

14:58.420 --> 15:00.370
Your father bound to you by blood.

15:02.180 --> 15:03.180
I was wrong.

15:05.490 --> 15:06.330
How about this?

15:06.490 --> 15:07.463
Cripple my martial arts.

15:08.340 --> 15:09.700
Imprison me.

15:09.700 --> 15:11.060
Let me suffer.

15:11.060 --> 15:12.130
Let me repent.

15:13.010 --> 15:13.890
Let me feel regret.

15:33.220 --> 15:34.420
You couldn't do it, so I did.

15:35.250 --> 15:36.983
I don't want his blood
to stain your hands.

15:57.890 --> 15:58.980
Grandfather.

16:00.300 --> 16:01.140
Uncle.

16:01.700 --> 16:02.540
Mother.

16:03.770 --> 16:04.770
I have

16:05.180 --> 16:06.020
avenged you.

16:07.420 --> 16:08.820
May your spirits in heaven

16:10.220 --> 16:11.130
rest in peace.

16:36.060 --> 16:36.900
Li, Xuankong Nunnery

16:37.130 --> 16:38.700
has long withdrawn from the world.

16:39.010 --> 16:40.530
Why did you massacre everyone?

16:40.820 --> 16:41.940
Because they did

16:42.300 --> 16:44.010
the most hateful thing in this world.

16:44.490 --> 16:46.490
Those hermits deserve death.

16:46.890 --> 16:48.420
What kind of absurd logic is that?

16:48.420 --> 16:50.700
Uncle Cheng and my master
died mysteriously.

16:51.060 --> 16:52.340
But when they were buried,

16:53.623 --> 16:55.716
those so-called righteous sects
didn't dare question

16:55.980 --> 16:58.180
because Yin Dai was the Lord

16:58.980 --> 17:00.490
of the foremost sect.

17:01.340 --> 17:02.220
That day,

17:02.220 --> 17:04.940
heroes gathered
atop the Thousandfold Cliff.

17:05.860 --> 17:07.700
In the end, only Cai Pingshu

17:07.700 --> 17:08.900
dared to speak up for justice.

17:09.330 --> 17:10.570
The matter was strange.

17:10.860 --> 17:12.090
Do you still remember?

17:12.090 --> 17:13.010
Indeed.

17:14.250 --> 17:16.770
Only Pingshu questioned it at that time.

17:17.180 --> 17:18.730
Others also felt something was odd,

17:18.730 --> 17:20.090
but out of courtesy,

17:20.090 --> 17:21.380
they could not say much.

17:25.290 --> 17:27.420
How laughable.

17:28.570 --> 17:30.220
Thousands of heroes

17:30.980 --> 17:32.660
were not as brave as a woman.

17:32.940 --> 17:34.470
I know there is hatred in your heart.

17:34.760 --> 17:35.620
But you can't...

17:35.620 --> 17:36.660
What?

17:36.660 --> 17:37.966
Now, I stand alone in this world.

17:38.700 --> 17:39.860
I have nothing left to fear.

17:40.330 --> 17:42.140
After my master and uncle's funeral,

17:42.660 --> 17:44.250
Yin Dai used revenge as an excuse

17:44.250 --> 17:46.090
to incite my fellow disciples

17:46.090 --> 17:48.010
to fight the demonic sect to the death.

17:48.010 --> 17:49.530
Even though they were outnumbered,

17:50.730 --> 17:52.900
he still forced them to go die.

17:54.050 --> 17:54.890
If they refused,

17:56.290 --> 17:57.810
they were called ungrateful,

17:59.900 --> 18:01.730
accused of betraying
their master's grace.

18:05.810 --> 18:07.010
In just two short years,

18:07.660 --> 18:10.180
I watched as my fellow disciples,

18:11.660 --> 18:12.730
wave after wave,

18:13.660 --> 18:15.250
went to their deaths.

18:16.860 --> 18:18.180
No one spoke up for them.

18:20.530 --> 18:21.570
In the end,

18:23.420 --> 18:24.810
only I remained.

18:24.810 --> 18:25.940
I know you are in pain.

18:28.010 --> 18:30.090
But Yin Dai is the real culprit.

18:30.090 --> 18:31.980
Why drag Chang into this?

18:32.730 --> 18:34.010
Back at the funeral,

18:34.570 --> 18:35.810
my father was not present.

18:36.220 --> 18:37.206
He knew nothing about it.

18:37.530 --> 18:38.900
What did he do wrong?

18:39.180 --> 18:40.490
Why did you kill him?

18:40.940 --> 18:42.620
That doesn't mean he was innocent.

18:43.090 --> 18:44.180
Those who died...

18:44.490 --> 18:45.700
Who among you remembers them?

18:46.380 --> 18:47.220
Li,

18:47.770 --> 18:49.420
since you remember Pingshu's kindness,

18:49.420 --> 18:51.490
can't you, for her sake,

18:51.490 --> 18:52.620
let this go?

18:53.090 --> 18:53.930
Xiaofeng,

18:55.420 --> 18:56.860
others may not know,

18:56.860 --> 18:58.570
but you should understand.

18:58.570 --> 19:01.530
Everything Yunke and I are doing now

19:01.530 --> 19:03.490
is for Cai Pingshu.

19:03.490 --> 19:05.290
The people you protect

19:05.290 --> 19:07.940
watched as Cai Pingshu

19:07.940 --> 19:09.380
went alone to Mount Tu

19:09.380 --> 19:11.140
to kill Nie Hengcheng.

19:11.140 --> 19:13.380
While she risked her life
fighting alone,

19:13.380 --> 19:14.940
what were they doing?

19:14.940 --> 19:16.140
One by one, they hid safely

19:16.140 --> 19:18.330
in their own corners,

19:18.330 --> 19:20.980
watching her risk her life for them.

19:20.980 --> 19:21.980
Stop talking.

19:22.810 --> 19:24.530
When my sister went alone to Mount Tu,

19:24.530 --> 19:25.980
it was her own choice.

19:26.570 --> 19:28.090
She never regretted it.

19:28.490 --> 19:29.330
So,

19:30.660 --> 19:33.180
no one needs to seek justice
on her behalf.

19:34.250 --> 19:36.290
Today, I only have one thing to say.

19:36.290 --> 19:38.250
Tell Qi Yunke to come out.

19:39.730 --> 19:41.330
I'll speak to him face-to-face.

19:41.660 --> 19:42.860
In that case,

19:44.330 --> 19:46.250
let death decide the outcome.

20:22.330 --> 20:23.170
Master.

20:24.090 --> 20:24.930
Master,

20:25.050 --> 20:26.730
they're breaking in. What to do?

20:26.730 --> 20:27.570
Why panic?

20:27.860 --> 20:30.090
Once I reach the final level,

20:30.090 --> 20:31.090
those clowns outside

20:31.570 --> 20:32.620
will be nothing to fear.

20:33.530 --> 20:34.370
Master,

20:35.010 --> 20:36.180
you don't look well.

20:36.900 --> 20:38.490
Give me two Purging Pills.

20:46.900 --> 20:47.740
Why?

20:48.220 --> 20:49.770
I've always treated you well.

20:49.770 --> 20:51.530
Pingshu even saved your life.

20:52.530 --> 20:53.900
Why did you do this?

20:53.900 --> 20:55.330
I can't watch you

20:55.330 --> 20:56.570
commit another grave mistake.

20:57.180 --> 20:59.660
You've already killed Lady Yin.

20:59.660 --> 21:01.010
Spare Lingbo.

21:01.010 --> 21:02.250
All for that woman?

21:02.860 --> 21:03.940
That cold-blooded,

21:03.940 --> 21:04.780
selfish,

21:05.140 --> 21:06.620
hypocritical woman?

21:06.620 --> 21:08.490
You'd betray Pingshu and me for her?

21:19.940 --> 21:20.780
Master,

21:21.180 --> 21:22.290
you and Ms. Cai

21:22.290 --> 21:23.940
gave me a second life.

21:25.380 --> 21:26.860
If you command it,

21:27.570 --> 21:29.090
I'd give my life without hesitation.

21:29.770 --> 21:30.610
However,

21:31.530 --> 21:33.420
one's conscience

21:33.980 --> 21:36.700
can never truly be extinguished.

21:39.380 --> 21:40.220
Master,

21:40.530 --> 21:41.490
Ms. Cai would never wish

21:41.980 --> 21:44.980
to see you slay your kin for revenge.

21:47.090 --> 21:48.140
Forgive me!

22:13.980 --> 22:15.140
Dalou.

22:15.140 --> 22:16.570
Take Lingbo and leave.

22:17.090 --> 22:17.930
Hurry!

22:22.860 --> 22:23.700
Dalou.

22:24.860 --> 22:26.090
Go.

22:48.570 --> 22:50.220
Go!

23:13.770 --> 23:15.380
Veilbreaker.

23:16.730 --> 23:18.380
You've mastered it.

23:23.900 --> 23:25.140
Kill me.

23:40.050 --> 23:40.890
Watch out!

24:09.740 --> 24:11.020
(Righteous Spirit)

24:32.090 --> 24:32.940
Zhao,

24:32.940 --> 24:34.140
give Lingbo to me.

24:35.490 --> 24:37.090
I'm almost there.

24:37.490 --> 24:38.330
Master,

24:39.090 --> 24:40.290
wake up.

24:40.290 --> 24:41.620
You'll get her killed!

24:41.620 --> 24:43.010
Give her to me.

24:48.090 --> 24:49.570
Forgive me.

25:02.090 --> 25:03.700
You're just like Mu Zhengyang.

25:04.250 --> 25:05.900
A skin-painted demon.

25:06.620 --> 25:08.140
Constantly bewitching Zhao.

25:08.620 --> 25:09.490
Otherwise,

25:09.810 --> 25:11.250
why would she get involved in this

25:11.730 --> 25:13.700
and suffer the lashes?

25:20.010 --> 25:21.010
Master,

25:22.140 --> 25:23.530
he's never harmed me.

25:24.810 --> 25:26.420
Please don't hurt him.

25:26.420 --> 25:27.860
He almost got you killed!

25:28.220 --> 25:29.060
If not for him,

25:29.420 --> 25:31.080
I wouldn't have used
the Withered Branch.

25:31.313 --> 25:32.982
Nor would there have been
all the trouble

25:32.993 --> 25:34.103
because of the Night Orchid.

25:34.490 --> 25:36.490
I wouldn't have needed to use

25:36.490 --> 25:37.770
corpse slaves to lure

25:37.770 --> 25:39.530
Song Xiuzhi and Yang Heying.

25:40.420 --> 25:41.570
Master,

25:43.010 --> 25:44.180
think about Aunt.

25:44.570 --> 25:46.420
You've spent your whole life
avenging her.

25:46.940 --> 25:47.940
Yet you committed

25:48.420 --> 25:50.090
the act of refining corpse slaves.

25:51.220 --> 25:52.530
Can you face her with that?

25:52.530 --> 25:54.900
If I didn't do this,
that'd be betraying Pingshu.

25:55.810 --> 25:57.180
Pingshu is already dead.

25:57.660 --> 25:58.620
These people

25:58.900 --> 25:59.940
don't deserve to live.

26:01.290 --> 26:02.810
If not for you,

26:02.810 --> 26:05.010
Nie Zhe would've long helped me
wipe out the Six Sects.

26:05.010 --> 26:06.420
Then I could kill Nie Zhe in turn

26:07.050 --> 26:09.660
and hand this clean Jianghu

26:09.660 --> 26:11.250
to Zhao and Yuzhi.

26:13.090 --> 26:14.770
Since you love meddling so much,

26:15.180 --> 26:16.530
I'll grant your wish

26:17.180 --> 26:18.490
and send you on your way.

26:19.330 --> 26:20.170
No!

26:23.140 --> 26:24.490
Why do you have no internal power?

26:25.503 --> 26:27.660
Didn't your father pass
all his internal power to you?

26:27.660 --> 26:29.380
I never expected you

26:29.380 --> 26:31.330
to covet my family's things as well.

26:31.330 --> 26:32.730
Unfortunately,

26:33.530 --> 26:35.330
I've given it to someone else.

26:35.330 --> 26:37.010
Useless!

26:40.980 --> 26:41.820
No!

27:15.860 --> 27:16.770
Stop.

27:17.530 --> 27:18.660
Don't keep making mistakes.

27:19.700 --> 27:20.620
I'm not wrong.

27:22.380 --> 27:23.380
I'm not.

27:23.810 --> 27:25.090
I must avenge my master,

27:26.050 --> 27:26.890
my uncle,

27:28.050 --> 27:29.660
and my fellow disciples.

27:30.140 --> 27:31.080
It's been over a decade.

27:31.420 --> 27:32.260
The world

27:32.620 --> 27:34.490
no longer remembers their names.

27:38.140 --> 27:39.050
But I remember.

27:48.380 --> 27:49.810
Ms. Cai was broad-minded.

27:53.140 --> 27:54.490
But I can't do the same.

28:12.250 --> 28:13.180
Wenxun, don't!

28:30.900 --> 28:31.860
Master!

28:34.900 --> 28:35.740
Master!

28:37.860 --> 28:38.700
Master!

28:49.900 --> 28:50.740
Master...

28:51.860 --> 28:52.810
Master...

30:35.620 --> 30:36.660
Master,

30:36.660 --> 30:38.140
you have to kill me first.

30:58.250 --> 30:59.090
Father.

30:59.090 --> 31:00.900
(Pillar of Jianghu)

31:03.700 --> 31:04.660
Let them go.

31:05.620 --> 31:06.700
Otherwise,

31:06.700 --> 31:08.420
you'll never master the Ziwei Method.

31:29.810 --> 31:31.490
The Disintegration.

31:36.700 --> 31:37.570
Master,

31:38.700 --> 31:39.900
stop.

32:12.810 --> 32:13.700
Master,

32:14.980 --> 32:16.490
Aunt once said

32:17.140 --> 32:18.620
that having a conscience

32:19.700 --> 32:22.250
matters more than following rules.

32:23.490 --> 32:24.530
And now,

32:25.220 --> 32:26.940
for the sake of Jianghu rules,

32:27.570 --> 32:29.330
you've thrown away your conscience.

32:32.180 --> 32:33.020
Have you

32:36.180 --> 32:37.570
forgotten all of it?

33:07.180 --> 33:08.860
A skin-painted demon.

33:42.730 --> 33:44.770
You're not a skin-painted demon.

34:05.380 --> 34:06.220
Zhao.

34:07.940 --> 34:09.130
Master.

34:11.690 --> 34:12.860
I'm sorry.

34:18.570 --> 34:20.050
Send me

34:23.690 --> 34:25.530
to see your aunt.

35:46.090 --> 35:46.930
Yunke.

35:48.130 --> 35:48.970
Pingshu.

36:47.700 --> 36:54.180
(Past and Future Glory)

37:00.001 --> 37:10.661
=Generation to Generation=

37:29.421 --> 37:33.831
♪The breeze is gentle,
and spring is fair♪

37:34.396 --> 37:39.011
♪I roam the rivers and hills
in the martial world♪

37:39.351 --> 37:43.916
♪With a shining cup,
I drink with delight tonight♪

37:44.441 --> 37:48.741
♪Free to wander in the world♪

37:51.686 --> 37:56.386
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

37:56.911 --> 38:01.201
♪I rest beneath the stars' soft gleam♪

38:01.861 --> 38:05.891
♪The night is calm, still as a stream♪

38:06.206 --> 38:11.331
♪It washes away all judgment and scheme♪

38:11.906 --> 38:16.716
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

38:16.931 --> 38:21.101
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

38:21.826 --> 38:25.761
♪I freely roam in the world♪

38:26.261 --> 38:31.536
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪

38:54.266 --> 38:59.396
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

38:59.761 --> 39:04.131
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

39:04.396 --> 39:08.526
♪I freely roam in the world♪

39:08.711 --> 39:14.286
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪
